1.1 Add a selected stock
Format: SCORPIO STOCK ADD {stock code}
Example: SCORPIO STOCK ADD sh600476
1.2 Remove a selected stock
Format: SCORPIO STOCK REM {stock code}
Example: SCORPIO STOCK REM sh600476
1.3 List all selected stocks
Format: SCORPIO STOCK LST

2.1 Add a trade
Format: SCORPIO TRADE ADD {stock code} [BUY|SELL] {price} {quantity} {time (HH:mm)}
Example: SCORPIO TRADE ADD sh600476 BUY 28.90 1000 14:23
2.2 Remove a trade
Format: SCORPIO TRADE REM {stock code} [BUY|SELL] {price} {quantity} {time (HH:mm)}
Example: SCORPIO TRADE REM sh600476 BUY 28.90 1000 14:23

3.1 List current position (including PnL)
Format: SCORPIO POSITION LST
3.2 Add position
Format: SCORPIO POSITION ADD {stock code} {quantity} {cost}
Example: SCORPIO POSITION ADD sh600362 5000 20.15
3.3 Remove position
Format: SCORPIO POSITION REM {stock code}
Example: SCORPIO POSITION REM sh600362

4.1 Start price feed
Format: SCORPIO PRICEFEED START
4.2 Stop price feed
Format: SCORPIO PRICEFEED STOP
4.3 Make price feed to reload selected stocks
Format: SCORPIO PRICEFEED RELOAD
4.4 Check price feed status (busy or idle)
Format: SCORPIO PRICEFEED STATUS

5.1 Add cash
Format: SCORPIO CASH ADD {amount} {time (HH:mm)}
Example: SCORPIO CASH ADD 100000 13:50
5.2 Remove cash
Format: SCORPIO CASH REM {amount} {time (HH:mm)}
Example: SCORPIO CASH REM 50000 14:35
5.3 List cash
Format: SCORPIO CASH LST
Example: SCORPIO CASH LST